&lt;p&gt;The first app is a basic website with simple routing. You can see source code at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/rafalmoneta/basic-site-express&quot;&gt;github repository&lt;/a&gt;. Also on day 7, I spend some time reading about Web Architecture, Client-Server Architecture and different tiers in software architecture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The second project is a simple message board created with Expressjs. Source code at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/rafalmoneta/mini-message-board&quot;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;. I deployed this app to Heroku and you can see a live demo &lt;a href=&quot;https://safe-bastion-00302.herokuapp.com/&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
