&lt;h2&gt;How to hide sensitive data in .env file&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a file called .env in the root of your project’s directory.
&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 197px;&quot;
    &gt;
